                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-16-victim158 t18220911-16-viclabel80"></join>. On the 8th of August, about eleven o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came into the passage - I saw him come from the larder, where the silver skewer was, in a fillet of veal. He is a sweep. I enquired at the bar, then ran after him, and overtook him and another sweep. I asked what business he had in the house? he said he called to see if any chimneys wanted sweeping. I asked what he had under his arm, and saw the skewer drop from him.</p>
